(80, 'aalee10@asu.edu', 'Alexander Lee', 'CS/E-025 Expeditise - Website Development: Streamlining Access to Information and Services', 'Expeditise is an assistance based website meant to quickly find an expert to solve a user\'s problem.  The key difference with Expeditise is the usage of AI via the GPT API in order to automatically search for the best fit for a given task. The project focused on front-end web design and back-end connections to offer a seemless communication system.', 'Ali Sarabi, asarabi1@asu.edu', 5, 'Alexander Lee, Nengcong Guan, Luke Dujmic, Andy Vu, Jerin Joseph', 'CSE486, CSE424', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/pJo6w-79bu8&ab_channel', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pJo6w-79bu8&ab_channel=AlexanderLee', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(81, 'sozgur@asu.edu', 'Spencer Ozgur', 'CS/E-044 Local Grow Salads - Director', 'Served as Database Architect for LGS. Worked with SQL and Postgres to manage database.', 'Kamna Surjani', 1, 'Spencer Ozgur', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/odNBMXEnOXg', 'https://youtu.be/odNBMXEnOXg', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(82, 'aareddy1@asu.edu', 'Abhikya Reddy Ananth', 'CS/E-048 Local Grown Salads - LGS EcoSystem Customer Layer', 'The Local Grown Salads (LGS) project aims to create customer-facing applications for distributors, retailers, manufacturers, and consumers. These tools enable real-time quality checks, feedback, and seamless data integration. The project ensures scalability, security, and an improved user experience using modern technologies like React Native', 'Zale Tabakman', 4, 'Noah McClleland, Abhikya Reddy Ananth, Daniel Olma, Eyasu Abebe', 'CSE 424, CSE 486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/7NuvmpoC_xo', 'https://youtu.be/7NuvmpoC_xo', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(83, 'amellio5@asu.edu', 'Aften Elliott', 'CS/E-068 SCAI - ASU Capstone Judging Application', 'The ASU Capstone Judging Application is a web platform designed to judge different events happening within ASU.', 'Steven Osburn', 3, 'Aften Elliott, Bharathi Chikkala, Janvi Siddhapura', 'CSE486', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/ozzlzX-GVPQ', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ozzlzX-GVPQ', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(84, 'mghasib@asu.edu', 'Majed Ghasib', 'CS/E-042 Local Grow Salads - Agronomist', 'The project involves developing a backend API to manage product packaging data by retrieving, adding, and displaying product and package details. It integrates data from the Product, Product Packaging, and related tables to ensure accurate connections between products and their associated packaging. The system aims to streamline the management and retrieval of product packaging information for further processing or display on a frontend application.', 'zale@localgrownfoods.ca', 1, 'Majed Ghasib', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/WLiMYpL4iV8', 'https://youtu.be/WLiMYpL4iV8', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(85, 'vpattela@asu.edu', 'Venkaata', 'CS/E-018 Center for Entrepreneurship and New Business Design - Housing Coordination', 'Our project involves creating a user-friendly website designed to connect Success Coaches and Housing Providers with Young Adults seeking housing. The platform will feature tools for listing housing options, filtering based on individual needs, and facilitating direct communication between providers and young adults. By streamlining the process, our website aims to support young adults in finding secure, suitable housing while improving collaboration between coaches and providers.', 'Larry Heitz', 5, 'Venkata Pattela, Kaylem Brown Malone, Nandini Singh,Christopher Hernandez, Duc Quang Tran', 'CSE486', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/5VSFSLv0fds', 'https://youtu.be/5VSFSLv0fds', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(86, 'tpauga@asu.edu', 'Tuliloa Pauga', 'CS/E-085 VariableAI - VariableAI - Group A', 'This machine learning model involves analyzing essays to create detailed profiles by capturing features such as writing style, vocabulary usage, and tone. These profiles are then used to generate new writing content based on the identified characteristics. This combines natural language processing with creative AI techniques for personalized content generation.', 'Vikash Suthapali, Mahesh Gali', 3, 'Yi-Shiang Chiu, Zachary Hayes', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/aFdfVJdZw9w', 'https://youtu.be/aFdfVJdZw9w', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(87, 'jrtint@asu.edu', 'Joshua Tint', 'CS/E-035 Honeywell International - CICT Code migration from Visual Basic to Python using Gen AI', 'Our project focuses on automating the process of transferring data from C++ files into an MS Access database. We are developing AI tools to parse and organize the C++ data for seamless integration into the database. A key goal is to make the process user-friendly by building a simple graphical user interface (GUI) that highlights errors and assists with debugging. This system will improve efficiency by simplifying data transfer and ensuring flexibility for different data formats. The overall aim is to create an automated solution that minimizes manual effort while handling complex data structures effectively.', 'Brendan Tyler Lasley - Honeywell', 5, 'Joshua Tint, Wallace Yopp, Matthew Rutherford, Geoffrey Grossthal, Elise Macabou', 'CSE 486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lleLODsAPDE', 'https://youtu.be/lleLODsAPDE', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(88, 'eaaguil3@asu.edu', 'Efren Aguilar', 'CS/E-028 Fourcher Technologies - Using AR to simulate the visual symptoms of dementia', 'The AR application we developed was designed to simulate the visual symptoms associated with dementia, enhancing understanding and empathy through immersive augmented reality experiences. Built for the Oculus Quest using Unity, the project incorporates features like dynamic symptom visualization and user-friendly interfaces to ensure accessibility and impact. Its development reflects a commitment to leveraging technology for educational and healthcare purposes.', 'Jordan Foucher', 5, 'Jack Hael, Agustin Ballesteros, Anushka Singh, Efren Aguilar, Joseph Kharzo', 'CSE 486', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/0jSZpkBOApo', 'https://youtu.be/0jSZpkBOApo', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(89, 'mradmard@asu.edu', 'Haroon Radmard', 'CS/E-069 SCAI - ASU Capstone Time Management', 'The SCAI - ASU Capstone Time Management website is a centralized platform designed to streamline project management for capstone students, faculty, and sponsors. It offers core functionalities like managing projects, backlog items, sprints, and assignments, alongside collaboration tools such as communication pages and a calendar. This platform enhances transparency, accountability, and efficiency while addressing limitations of third-party tools.', 'Steven Osburn', 4, 'Madison McGuire, Haroon Radmard, Wejdan Alharthi, and Kelly Raines', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/R_S0b3FSa3s', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R_S0b3FSa3s', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(90, 'jwfrey@asu.edu', 'Jesse Frey', 'CS/E-005 Allennials at Work Inc. - Apple API Development for Publishing a WordPress Digital Magazine', 'A chatbot application for Allennials At Work that is ran locally on an employees machine. This application fetches answers from a secure server hosted by a Allenials at work server machine using Ollama 3.2.', 'Clair Kim', 3, 'Jesse Frey, Wenqi Liu, Timothy Gonzales', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/sRrLrIskODI', 'https://youtu.be/sRrLrIskODI', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(91, 'sberdia@asu.edu', 'Sohum Berdia', 'CS/E-037 InnC LLC - ArtVision Visualizer', 'Artwork AR Visualizer App that let\'s you generate and showcase artowork on your wall using your phone and AI.', 'Priyanka Khati', 2, 'Sohum Berdia, Derek Sanchez', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/kXSP6-LfBuA', 'https://youtu.be/kXSP6-LfBuA', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(92, 'cnguye61@asu.edu', 'Christina Nguyen', 'CS/E-051 Lower 22 Foundation Inc - Foxhole Lounge Mobile App Redesign', 'Our project involved redesigning a social media app for veterans. The goal is to create an easy to navigate application that helps foster a sense of community amongst veterans. The app will be available on both IOS and Android systems.', 'Adam Nance, Jennifer Mena', 4, 'Christina Nguyen, Jared Kitchen, Jasmine Miller, Trenton Cerny', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/uynR011qeM8', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uynR011qeM8', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(93, 'pgibbon4@asu.edu', 'Ping Gibbons', 'CS/E-057 Ofori - Enhancing Ofori\'s Website and Expanding Services', 'This web development project supervised by our sponsor Daniella Addison, involved enhancing the current functionalities of Ofori’s website by implementing a user feedback system and blog section. These additions aim to improve user engagement and satisfaction by facilitating effective communication between Ofori and its users.', 'Daniella Addison (oforibeautyy@gmail.com)', 2, 'Ping Gibbons, Aiden Robins', 'CSE486', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/VDpOnAgutsE', 'https://youtu.be/VDpOnAgutsE', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(94, 'kkangas1@asu.edu', 'Kayla Kangas', 'CS/E-073 Self Justice Inc. - WordPress Website Development', 'Our project is Self Justice Inc, a website that allows Canadians to get a fair outcome in divorce proceedings without having to pay for an expensive attorney. The primary objective of this capstone project was to enhance the functionality, user experience, and performance of the Self Justice website.', 'Kyle Lacroix', 5, 'Alexander Epolite, Kayla Kangas, Jacky Situ, Victor Nyalita, Lawson Woods', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/0p2du3h_4zM', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0p2du3h_4zM', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(95, 'hkumar30@asu.edu', 'Harsh Kumar', 'CS/E-088 Velocity Tech Inc. - Zinio TalentHub', 'Zinio TalentHub is an innovative platform designed to streamline the process of connecting businesses with ERP-specialized contractors. With features like AI-powered resume parsing algorithms and contractor profile creation, Zinio ensures that companies can quickly find the best-fit contractors.', 'Strive Mazunga', 4, 'Harsh Kumar, Julia Kereszturi, Gunakarthik Naidu Lanka, Peshal Srinivas Kanamaluru', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/zHi9HdFdgHA', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zHi9HdFdgHA', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(96, 'rlin28@asu.edu', 'Ronald Lin', 'CS/E-023 DigiClips - Media Search Engine - Team 1', 'nhance user experience by providing a robust system for scouring the internet for media mention. By leveraging modern web technologies and cloud services Seamless and scalable solution for digital content management, empowering businesses and individuals to efficiently handle their media assets.', 'DigiClips Media Search Engine', 2, 'Ronald Lin, Rishon D. Netala', 'CSE 486', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/JJd-DC17lxQ', 'https://youtu.be/JJd-DC17lxQ', '2024-11-23', 'YES'),
(97, 'wlee90@asu.edu', 'WeiChieh Lee', 'CS/E-017 Carnival Guide - Carnival Guide', 'A web platform for exploring global carnivals, purchasing Mas Camp costumes,  and booking merchandise.', 'L.Baptiste', 4, 'WeiChieh Lee, Suvan Kumar, Dan Nguyen, Isaiah Elder', 'CSE486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/CQM9g1Rgl-Y&t', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CQM9g1Rgl-Y&t=3s', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(98, 'spande49@asu.edu', 'Smrita Pandey', 'CS/E-053 Naralytics - Mobile App Re-Design (React Native)', 'Nara is to enhance emotional intelligence and relational well-being by helping users understand the emotions and perspectives of themselves and their loved ones. By creating characters and stories that mirror real-life conflicts, Nara provides insights into the reasons behind certain behaviors and potential reactions.', 'Gyou-Re Lee', 3, 'SMRITA PANDEY, MD SALMAN RAHMAN, RACHAEL WEBB', 'CSE 486, CSE 424', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/shorts', 'https://youtu.be/CEUED2B7Itc', '2024-11-23', 'NO'),
(99, 'nkamble@asu.edu', 'Nina Kamble', 'CS/E-052 Naralytics - iOS / Android App New Features', 'Naralytics enhances user engagement by exploring emotions and perspectives, with features like streamlined character creation, auto-save functionality, redesigned user interface and automated summary generation.', 'Gyou-Re Lee', 3, 'Nina Kamble, Saatvik Rao, Jay Patel', 'CSE 486', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/L3Ka4IVir1o', 'https://youtu.be/L3Ka4IVir1o', '2024-11-23', 'NO');
